### B&Y Technology API Tests

@host = http://localhost:8080
@email = admin@bnytechnologies.com
@password = admin

### Login (Returns HttpOnly Cookie)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Get Current User (Requires Cookie)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/me

### Logout
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/logout

### Public: Get Products
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products

### Public: Submit Contact Form (Lead)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "message": "I'd like to learn more about your services."
}

### Admin: Get All Leads (Requires Cookie)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/admin/leads

### Admin: Update Company Info
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/admin/company-info
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "legalName": "B & Y Technology Inc.",
  "tagline": "Next-Gen Retail Software",
  "aboutText": "Updated about text.",
  "foundedYear": 2015,
  "headquarters": "San Francisco",
  "email": "hello@bnytechnologies.com",
  "phone": "+1 555 000 0000"
}
